This PR is to add a challenge according to my GSOC proposal,
Students need to code a way out of the maze tackle zombies

Todo:
- [x] Unittest to grade 
- [x] Code clean up and setting up of goals
- [x] function which will check of the code successfully worked or not
- [x] preferred logic

- [x] Functions follow underscore notation
- [x] Spell check done & typos fixed

- [x] Reviewers assigned (all peers & at least 1 mentor)

## Summary
This is how the new pyscript component looks like
its added to the index just for showing, once approved will be removed from there

The black area is the terminal where the output will be printed.
We can run the program either by clicking the green run button or
pressing `shift + enter` on the keyboard

Features:
- Auto indentation
- Keyword suggestion
